    <p style="color: aliceblue;">
      hmm behen… dekho, tumhe shayad lagta hoga ki koi insan online kisi pe itna
      trust kaise kar sakta hai… ya itni jaldi kisi ko apna kaise maan sakta
      hai…<br /><br />

      par sach bolu na, kabhi kabhi dil ko bas ek apnapan chahiye hota hai…
      reason nahi.<br /><br />

      pata hai… mujhe hamesha se lagta tha ki life me maine sab kuch
      aadha-adhura kiya hai. na main ek perfect beta ban paya… na kisi ka
      favourite insan. gharwalo ne mere upar bahut kuch kharch kiya, bahut
      umeede rakhi… par jo mera sapna tha na… woh pura nahi hua.<br /><br />

      aur uske baad literally main andar se toot gaya tha. aisa phase tha ki
      lagbhag 2–2.5 saal tak ghar se properly bahar tak nahi nikla. dosti…
      rishte… sab chhod diye maine. na koi close friend… na kisi se dil ki baat.
      bas room, silence aur main.<br /><br />

      aur funny baat pata hai kya hai? insan bahar se normal acting kar leta
      hai… par andar se woh wahi ruk jata hai jahan uska dil toota tha.<br /><br />

      ab thoda normal hua hu… thoda hass leta hu… thoda baat kar leta hu… par
      haan, thoda sa “physo” toh shayad ab bhi hu.<br /><br />

      “jo log andar se zyada feel karte hai na… woh bahar se thode ajeeb lagte
      hi hai.”<br /><br />

      aur ek baat bolu… bachpan se mann karta tha ki meri bhi ek behen hoti.
      jiske liye bina wajah gifts lene ka mann kare… jiske liye sacrifice karne
      ka mann kare… jisse ye feel ho ki “haan, koi apna hai.”<br /><br />

      tumhe shayad ye sab immature lage… par main genuinely woh emotions feel
      karna chahta tha jo shayad mujhe kabhi mile hi nahi.<br /><br />

      aur jab tumne bola tha na — “bhai banoge?” toh maine instantly “haan”
      bolne ka reason yhi tha. kyuki pata nahi kyu… mujhe laga shayad tumhe bhi
      ek genuine bhai chahiye hoga.<br /><br />

      par baad me samjha… tum kaafi alag ho. tum chill ho… unpredictable ho… aur
      honestly kaafi mature bhi. tumari ek baat muje kaffi achhi lagti ho ki tum
      kafi honest person ho.<br /><br />

      aur pata hai… wo kehte hai na — “bhookhe insan ko chatni-roti bhi shahi
      khana lagti hai…” toh shayad meri zindagi me jo bhook thi na… woh pyaar
      aur sukoon shayad tum hi ho.<br /><br />

      tashuu ne ek baat bahut sahi boli thi — “Kabhi kabhi insan cheeze dusro ke
      liye nahi… khud ke satisfaction ke liye karta hai.”<br /><br />

      toh shayad main bhi wahi kar raha hu. isliye agar maine tumhe behen bola
      hai… toh hamesha behen hi bolunga.<br /><br />

      aur haan, main possessive-vossessive nahi hu. meri tone thodi ajeeb hogi
      bas.<br /><br />

      par ek baat dil se — tum life me kisi se bhi baat karo… kisi ke saath bhi
      raho… chahe tumhe meri zarurat ho ya na ho… main hamesha tumhare saath
      rahunga.<br /><br />

      “kabhi kabhi rishte khoon se nahi… sukoon se bante hai.”<br /><br />

      jab bhi lage ki koi nahi hai… bas awaaz de dena. main aa jaunga.<br /><br />

      baki chalo… shayad tum bore ho gayi hogi itna emotional lecture sunke.
      feedback zarur dena iska.<br /><br />

      aur haan… next wala page jo bhi ho… dil se karna okay?
      <strong>love you sister 💖 my princess… byeeeeee 🌸</strong>
    </p>
